snippet.title: Johnny Depp SPEAKS OUT About Being The Father Of Amber Heard's Daughter... ?!
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp SPEAKS OUT About Being The Father Of Amber Heard's Daughter... ?!
Over the past couple years, just about every single story about Amber Heard has been tied to her ongoing court case with Johnny Depp. We don't say that lightly, either, we know that this is a case that has been getting lots of attention due to the fact that both sides are desperate to go and get their own kind of vindication of sorts. That's due to the fact that each side is accusing the other of. But amongst all of this though is a small bright spot that none can ignore, because Amber Heard...has had a girl. We'll break it down for you. Be sure to like the video and subscribe to the channel!

Click HERE To Enter The GIVEAWAY! 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC76r9K-_Knc7d38c9uKRwaw?sub_confirmation=1 

And there you have it, everyone! A look at Amber Heard and how she "gave birth" to a daughter and all that it might mean for her going forward. Did you know that she was planning to have a child? Do you think that having this new life in her own life will change how she sees things and how she goes about handling Johnny Depp? Or do you think she'll see this as an opportunity to try and "twist the screws" one more time against Depp? Let us know in the comments below, be sure to subscribe and we'll see you next time on the channel!
